content: Both my sons (4 year age gap) love this game and it's provided them with a lot of entertainment over the years - I first bought this game in December 2013!  What I liked about it is that it's an educational game and ties in very nicely with the animated films, which they both enjoy as well.  As an added bonus, the only time I had an issue with being able to load the game, the customer service I received was wonderful. They were able to suggest a couple of ideas that pinpointed the issue I was having.  All in all, I highly recommend the game (good for ages 3 to 6/7) and thank the customer service staff for their help. :)
